UI patterns include   
》 elements like text, color, or icons;  
》 ​components, which are made up of elements, like a button or form label;   
》 ​modules, which are groups of components, ​like a header with a logo or a navigation bar at the top of the page;  
》 templates, which are groups of modules put together to form pages.  
